      <description>&lt;p&gt;An &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.metacritic.com/browse/albums/score/metascore/year/filtered?year_selected=2024&amp;amp;distribution=&amp;amp;sort=desc&amp;amp;view=detailed&#34;&gt;aggregate review site&lt;/a&gt; tells me that the top three albums of the year are
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/music/article/2024/jun/06/charli-xcx-brat-review-insecurity-obliterating-anthems-by-pops-most-human-superstar&#34;&gt;Brat by Charli XCX&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&#34;https://thequietus.com/quietus-reviews/album-of-the-week/songs-of-a-lost-world-the-cure-review/&#34;&gt;Songs for a Lost World by The Cure&lt;/a&gt;
